data.description: Welcome to 7 W 9th Street!  Located a block away from the Brick District & Westminster, this 2 Bed/2 Bath Home shines with character.   Mature trees and landscaping welcome you to the cozy front porch.  Charming archways, gleaming hardwood floors and brick fireplace add a special touch.  Spacious kitchen with white cabinets and plenty of counterspace.  Kitchen walks into mudroom with convenient main level laundry.   Large deck off kitchen is perfect for relaxing or entertaining.    Separate dining room w/hardwood floors. Large sized bedrooms w/updated bathroom. Primary bedroom offers two closets, warm paint colors and updated ceiling fan. Tons of storage in unfinished basement.This home is cute as a button & ready for the new owners! Showings start 11/24/23
